---
applyTo: "*started*.md"
---
- Always use the `_guide_template.md` as a template and create a copy from that
- Use the following file naming patter: `getting-started-[feature].md`
- Replace contents from the template with the appropriate content you are writing
- Always prioritize readability and clarity.
- Target new users to the platform
- Ask for clarification from the user about the actual content if not detailed enough
- Aim for providing an example on how to actually do the given task
- If there are multiple ways to achieve something, list the simplest one, mention others
- Link other pages if the reader want to learn more about a certain aspect of the product